<%= render partial: "main_header" %>

<%= video_tag "mentu2.webm", id: "video", autoplay: true, :loop => true %>
<div id="full-page">
	<div class="section1">
		<div class="section1-text-content">
			<div id="section1-title-text">
				Get Matched with Your Personal Mentors
			</div>
			<div id="section1-sub-text">
				Learn from 1000+ top college students
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mentor-sign-up-container">
			<div class="mentor-sign-up-text">
				We're currently taking mentor applications
			</div>
			<%= link_to '/auth/facebook' do %>
				<div class="btn mentor-apply-btn sign-up">
					<%= image_tag 'fbiconyellow.svg', :class => "fb-icon" %>
					<div id="mentor-apply-btn-text">Sign up to Apply</div>
				</div>
			<% end %>
		</div>
		<div class="student-signup no-mobile">
			<%= form_for @user do |f| %>
				<%= f.text_field :dream_school, :class => "landing-user-field", placeholder: "Dream School" %>
				<%= f.text_field :major, :class => "landing-user-field", placeholder: "Major" %>
				<%= f.text_field :email, :class => "landing-user-field", placeholder: "Email" %>
				<div class="landing-user-field submit">
						<%= image_tag 'fbicon.svg', :class=> "fb-icon" %> Sign Up
				</div>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section2">
		<div class="section2-title">
			Our mentors come from all over. Many from prestigious institutes.
		</div>
		<div id="places">
			<% (1..6).each do |place| %>
				<%= image_tag "school#{place}.png", :class => "place" %>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section3">
		<div class="section3-title">
			Here's how it works.
		</div>
		<div class="col-3-container">
			<div class="col-3">
				<%= image_tag 'howitworks1.svg', :class => "step-pic" %>
				<div class="step-title">1. Choose Your Interests</div>
				<div class="step-desc">Tell us what you're passionate about. You can get help for a TOEFL test, a job interview, or a startup pitch.</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-3">
				<%= image_tag 'howitworks2.svg', :class => "step-pic" %>
				<div class="step-title">2. Select Your Mentor</div>
				<div class="step-desc">Select mentors you like most based on their strengths, backgrounds, and availability. You can choose as many mentors as you like.</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-3">
				<%= image_tag 'howitworks3.svg', :class => "step-pic" %>
				<div class="step-title">3. Start Your Learning</div>
				<div class="step-desc">Log in when the session starts, and connect with your mentors as you go through your fully personalized curriculum.
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section4">
		<div class="section-title">Interested in becoming a mentor?</div>
		<div class="col-3-container">
			<div class="col-3">
				<div class="mentor-info-header">Responsibilities</div>
				<div class="mentor-info">
					College Search Advice<br>Experience Sharing<br>Essay Writing<br>Personal Growth
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-3">
				<div class="mentor-info-header">Benefits</div>
				<div class="mentor-info">
					Training<br>We pay $40/hr<br>$20 for every mentor you refer that gets accepted
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-3">
				<div class="mentor-info-header">Requirements</div>
				<div class="mentor-info">
					A paragraph summary about why you'd like to become a mentor<br>A 1 minute video telling us about yourself
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<%= link_to '/auth/facebook' do %>
			<div class="btn get-started sign-up">
				<%= image_tag 'fbiconyellow.svg', :class => "fb-icon" %>Sign up to apply
			</div>
		<% end %>
	</div>

	<div class="section5 no-mobile">
		<div class="section5-title">Get help applying to college</div>
		<div class="section5-sub-text">Tell us a bit about yourself so we can keep you in the loop when we launch.</div>
		<%= form_for @user do |f| %>
			<%= f.text_field :dream_school, :class => "landing-user-field", placeholder: "Dream School" %>
			<%= f.text_field :major, :class => "landing-user-field", placeholder: "Major" %>
			<%= f.text_field :email, :class => "landing-user-field", placeholder: "Email" %>
			<div class="landing-user-field submit">
					<%= image_tag 'fbicon.svg', :class=> "fb-icon" %> Sign Up
			</div>
		<% end %>
	</div>

	<div class="section6">
		<div class="section6-links">
			<div class="section6-link">About</div>
			<div class="section6-link">Terms & Conditions</div>
			<div class="section6-link">Privacy</div>
			<div class="section6-link">Contact Us</div>
		</div>
		<div class="about">
			Mentu helps students Umami Blue Bottle direct trade, cliche leggings keffiyeh crucifix art party sriracha food truck aesthetic fixie occupy +1. Selfies American Apparel Shoreditch, ennui XOXO twee four loko literally. Banjo meditation pop-up, wolf Marfa lumbersexual ugh Bushwick tofu 8-bit occupy semiotics. Cornhole crucifix lumbersexual Pitchfork mlkshk freegan.
		</div>
		<div class="copyright">
			Â©2014 Mentu. All Rights Reserved.
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

